## Bubble frontend environment
##
## Preferred setup: keep `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL` in repo root `.env`
## and run frontend via package scripts (`npm start`), which preload ../.env.
##
## Expo reads vars prefixed with `EXPO_PUBLIC_`.
##
## Recommended: leave this unset and the app will auto-detect local dev:
## - Android emulator -> http://10.0.2.2:4000/api
## - iOS simulator -> http://localhost:4000/api
## - Real device (same Wi‑Fi) -> http://<your-laptop-ip>:4000/api (derived from Expo host)
##
## If you need to override:
## EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://10.0.2.2:4000/api
## EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.50:4000/api
